## Acceptance Criteria

### 1. EAS config valid
```bash
cat mobile/eas.json | python3 -m json.tool > /dev/null && echo "eas.json: valid JSON OK"
```

### 2. All three build profiles present
```bash
python3 -c "
import json
config = json.load(open('mobile/eas.json'))
builds = config['build']
assert 'development' in builds
assert 'preview' in builds
assert 'production' in builds
print('Build profiles: OK')
"
```

### 3. Railway URL in all profiles
```bash
python3 -c "
import json
config = json.load(open('mobile/eas.json'))
url = 'https://flipper-production-dca0.up.railway.app/api/v1'
for profile in config['build'].values():
    assert profile.get('env', {}).get('EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL') == url
print('Railway URL in all profiles: OK')
"
```

### 4. app.json valid
```bash
cat mobile/app.json | python3 -m json.tool > /dev/null && echo "app.json: valid JSON OK"
```

